# API

## Auth

Navigate to /login to authenticate with Spotify. The JWT returned must be used as a bearer token for the requests below.

## Playlists

### Create

Creates a playlist from a Spotify playlist and returns its id.

```
POST /playlist
{
    "name": "{name}",
    "from": {
        "source": "spotify_playlist",
        "id": "{spotify_playlist_id}"
    }
}
```

## Game

### Create

Creates a game and returns its id.

```
POST /games
{
  "playlist_id": "{playlist_id}"
}
```

### Advance

Advances the game by one track returning the currently playing track.

```
POST /games/{gameId}/next
```
